          <div class="work-case__body">
            <p>SEO Studio analyzes real distributor pages, competitive exposure, AI-search readiness, and revenue-path opportunities.</p>
            <p>It does not stop at rankings. It gives executives the business answer first, then gives digital teams the workspace to inspect evidence, compare competitors, and approve work.</p>
